<p>
  <strong>2009-11-06</strong><br/>
  The phpMyFAQ Team would like to announce the availability of the first preview release of our next major version,
  <a href="/download">phpMyFAQ 2.6.0-alpha</a>, the "Pyotr Ilyich Tchaikovsky" release. In this release we
